data.description: WALK INTO EQUITY! This home is listed for $20k less than appraised value! See attached appraisal. This home has just undergone a full remodel, making it a TRUE GEM in Rowlett, Texas!  LOCATION!!  Lakeside location is key! You are just a 3-minute WALK from the beautiful Lake Ray Hubbard!  The kitchen is the heart of this home and boasts NEW Quartz Countertops, Stainless Steel Appliances, offering a sleek and modern space to host guests!  With a 2023 Roof and brand-new white paint, this home feels LIKE NEW!  The Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring spans the entire first floor, providing durability and elegance, while the New Carpet upstairs is sound-resistant and cozy!  Need extra storage?  No problem, as this property provides an enormous garage, attic space, and a remodeled shed in the backyard.  Come experience the charm of 8209 America’s Cup – a fully remodeled home that combines location, style, and value!
